From e790eeabc47cd4905606839fe3eb18df2bbd4d3e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrei Vagin <avagin@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 1 Feb 2019 14:20:24 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 49/55] kernel/exit.c: release ptraced tasks before
